data.description: Welcome to this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home, perfectly designed for comfortable and spacious living. This residence on a corner lot is in a desirable neighborhood and offers a harmonious blend of modern style and practical functionality.  As you step inside, you are greeted by a bright and inviting living area, boasting an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the living room, dining room, and kitchen. The abundant natural light cascades through large windows, creating an airy and cheerful ambiance.  The kitchen is a chef’s dream featuring sleek countertops, ample cabinet space, and modern appliances. The primary bedroom is a serene retreat, offering a peaceful sanctuary at the end of the day.  The additional three bedrooms are well-proportioned, offering comfort and privacy. Whether you’re seeking a place to raise your next generation or a spacious haven to call your own, this home presents an excellent opportunity for a fulfilling lifestyle.
